ğŸ¯ IMMEDIATE NEXT STEPS
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

1. VERIFY DEPENDENCIES (2 min)
   which tte && which jq && which alacritty
   
   If TTE missing: sudo pacman -S python-terminaltexteffects

2. CHOOSE ONE SETUP (seconds)
   Symphony: bash ~/setup-symphony-screensaver.sh
   Omarchy:  bash ~/setup-omarchy-screensaver.sh
   
3. RELOAD HYPRLAND (seconds)
   hyprctl reload
   
4. RESTART HYPRIDLE (seconds)
   pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &
   
5. TEST IT (optional)
   Manual: screensaver-launch
   Auto:   Wait 2.5 min without input


